{"id":13372,"date":"2024-02-10T18:53:16","date_gmt":"2020-08-10T13:23:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=13372"},"modified":"2023-05-30T00:52:58","modified_gmt":"2023-05-29T19:22:58","slug":"diy-bedroom-decor","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/diy-bedroom-decor\/","title":{"rendered":"DIY Decor Ideas For Your Bedroom"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Time to stop being lazy and start getting creative with these DIY bedroom decor ideas. What are you waiting for, let&#8217;s get you started!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Have a bedroom which had no life in it? It&#8217;s the plain old boring wall with a bed in the middle. Why fear? We at Design Cafe have ideas for you to let your wild child out.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Check Out Wall Art Ideas For Bedroom DIY&#8217;S<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have a bedroom with a slate wall well wake up! Don&#8217;t just leave it like that as you have an opportunity to create a masterpiece every day. Check out this DIY bedroom idea. This bedroom is a children&#8217;s bedroom with a single bed, wooden flooring and a beautifully woven floor mat in jute. A slate wall is a part of this <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom&#8217;s interior design<\/a> that allows your child and you to create DIY bedroom wall decor. Imagine having a new theme every day? Or just doodles of your child\u2019s wild imaginations and funny cartoons with motivational quotes? Cool right? Try this DIY bedroom wall decor out and let us know how it turns out.  <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10184223\/wall-art-ideas-for-bedroom-diy.jpg\" alt=\"A slate wall is a part of this bedroom's interior design that allows your child and you to create DIY bedroom wall decor.\" class=\"wp-image-13380\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10184223\/wall-art-ideas-for-bedroom-diy.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10184223\/wall-art-ideas-for-bedroom-diy-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10184223\/wall-art-ideas-for-bedroom-diy-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10184223\/wall-art-ideas-for-bedroom-diy-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A kids room with a slate wall and wooden flooring with  DIY bedroom wall decor<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, Explore more about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/diy-wall-art-ideas\/\">DIY Wall Art Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Crafty DIY Bedroom Ideas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If your child loves origami (the Japanese art of folding paper into decorative shapes and figures)&nbsp; then this DIY bedroom decor is sure to bring a smile on your child&#8217;s face. White walls can get pretty boring and mundane. So get some craft paper out and make a plain wall into a work of art.&nbsp; Create little cranes, planes, birds, crowns or whatever your child likes to make this wall more interactive. This DIY bedroom idea can be implemented in no time. This bedroom here has a white wall that\u2019s decorated with pretty birds made from origami paper.  <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10183705\/crafty-diy-bedroom-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"A white wall filled with cranes, planes, birds, made from origami paper is excellent bedroom wall decor ideas DIY.\" class=\"wp-image-13375\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10183705\/crafty-diy-bedroom-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10183705\/crafty-diy-bedroom-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10183705\/crafty-diy-bedroom-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10183705\/crafty-diy-bedroom-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Quirky DIY Bedroom Decor Crafts<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Time to fly high with these DIY bedroom decor crafts. This bedroom will remind you of a summer day with a clear blue sky that is perfect for flying some kites! Oh yes! Kites in a sweet little bedroom like this will leave your child in awe. If your child loves the colour blue then this bedroom is just perfect. With blue and white furniture that spells out calmness, there is only one more little thing that can make this room a little more creative. You&#8217;re right, it is a DIY bedroom decor craft. If you take a look at this wall, it would not have been interesting with DIY kites that make the wall seem like the sky. All you need is old pieces of cloth, cut them into diamond shapes. You can use coloured cardboard too and sticks as partitions. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10184116\/quirky-diy-bedroom-decor-crafts.jpg\" alt=\"Beautiful room with daybed and bean bag in blue and a white wall decorated with DIY kites are DIY bedroom decor crafts.\" class=\"wp-image-13379\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10184116\/quirky-diy-bedroom-decor-crafts.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10184116\/quirky-diy-bedroom-decor-crafts-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10184116\/quirky-diy-bedroom-decor-crafts-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10184116\/quirky-diy-bedroom-decor-crafts-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A beautiful room in blue with a matching daybed and bean bag brings in a calm vibe<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">DIY Bedroom Wall Decor<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This room is simply angelic in its look with a DIY home bed and fairy lights attached to it. The chandeliers are made of jute and this room has white flooring to match the interiors. To make this white wall a little more attractive, why not try DIY bedroom wall decor. All you have to do is add some polka dots. Yes, it&#8217;s as simple as that. With these little dots, your kids bedroom will look much prettier. Try it out.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10183914\/diy-bedroom-wall-decor.jpg\" alt=\"DIY bedroom ideas decorate a white wall with polka dot to make it more attractive.\" class=\"wp-image-13377\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10183914\/diy-bedroom-wall-decor.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10183914\/diy-bedroom-wall-decor-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10183914\/diy-bedroom-wall-decor-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10183914\/diy-bedroom-wall-decor-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A sweet room with a polka theme, a bed with plush star pillows and a blush quilt <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Regals On The Block: DIY Bedroom Ideas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Got some wood laying around? Time to stack up together. Check out this super cool DIY bedroom idea where you can make you own regals. Your mother told you not to waste food well we in the interior industry will tell you don&#8217;t waste wood or any other material. You can always make something out of waste. Take a look at this bedroom. It has got regals made from leftover wood planks! They look stunning and can give your room a hippie vibe. What do you say? All you need is some planks, glue, a hammer, a few nails and a measuring tape. Pretty easy, huh? You can paint these regals and make them in any shape you want. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10183602\/blocks-diy-decor-ideas-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"DIY bedroom decor with leftover wood planks turned into blocks look stunning and can give your room a hippie vibe.\" class=\"wp-image-13374\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10183602\/blocks-diy-decor-ideas-for-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10183602\/blocks-diy-decor-ideas-for-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10183602\/blocks-diy-decor-ideas-for-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10183602\/blocks-diy-decor-ideas-for-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A bedroom with DIY wooden regals that pep up the place with a little quirk<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">DIY Wall Painting Ideas For Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Rainbows, falling stars, winged horses across the skies to magical lands. These are all the things a little girl dreams of! Well, it&#8217;s time for some DIY wall painting ideas for the bedroom. Get with the little princess and bring out those pretty coloured paints and brushes for you will need them all to create a magical world on a white wall. This frosty white bedroom with matching furniture needs a sprinkle of magic. Take a look at this young girls bedroom wall that\u2019s painted with unicorns, rainbows, icecreams and drop lights shaped like cones. Takes you back to fairyland right? <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10184017\/diy-wall-painting-ideas-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"White walls with matching furniture &amp; paintings of yummy icecreams and unicorns are DIY bedroom makeover ideas.\" class=\"wp-image-13378\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10184017\/diy-wall-painting-ideas-for-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10184017\/diy-wall-painting-ideas-for-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10184017\/diy-wall-painting-ideas-for-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/10184017\/diy-wall-painting-ideas-for-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A snow-white bedroom with paintings of yummy icecreams and unicorns<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This is what we at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">Design Cafe<\/a> think are the best DIY decor ideas for bedrooms. Let us know what you think! Send us an email. Can&#8217;t wait to hear from you!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also Read:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/apartment-balcony-decor-ideas\/\">Apartment Balcony Decor Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/christmas-tree-decoration-ideas\/\">Christmas Tree Decorations Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/curtains-and-blinds-drapes-shades\/\">Shades For Windows<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/diy-crafts-for-home-decor\/\">DIY Crafts For Home Decor<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/diy-party-decoration-ideas\/\">DIY Party Decorations Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/eco-friendly-ganesh-chaturthi-decoration-ideas\/\">Eco Friendly Ganpati Decoration Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/friendship-day-decoration-ideas\/\">Friendship Day Decoration Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/garden-decor-ideas\/\">Home Garden Decor Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/gold-wallpaper-ideas\/\">Beautiful Gold Wallpaper Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/holi-decoration-ideas\/\">DIY Holi Decoration Ideas<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\